    App

    An evaluation strategy for analyzing and testing the behavior of chatbot simulation classes.
    ChatBotStrategy
    The ChatBotStrategy class evaluates a specified class by analyzing its fields based on defined criteria such as name, type, and modifiers.
    ConsoleLoggerObserver
    Observes the evaluation process and logs messages to the console.
    EvaluationObserver

    Defines a strategy for evaluating classes through test execution and feedback generation.
